title: Weight Lifting
discribe: Weight training is a common type of strength training for developing the strength and size of skeletal muscles.[2] It uses the force of gravity in the form of weighted bars, dumbbells or weight stacks in order to oppose the force generated by muscle through concentric or eccentric contraction.
